First --

00:00:09.330 --> 00:00:10.630
&gt;&gt; Alexandra Bracken:
Yey, wee [laughter]!

00:00:10.630 --> 00:00:11.930
&gt;&gt; Stephanie Merry:
First, a word of thanks

00:00:11.930 --> 00:00:14.200
