00:40:48.260 --> 00:40:49.560
&gt;&gt; Alexandra Bracken:
Jones, thank you.

00:40:49.560 --> 00:40:50.860
&gt;&gt; Stephanie Merry: Jones, yes.

00:40:50.860 --> 00:40:52.160
