00:41:09.680 --> 00:41:12.250
And every time they would
announce a new actor

00:41:12.250 --> 00:41:13.870
for the project,
I was like, "Oh,

00:41:13.870 --> 00:41:15.660
I never would have
thought of that person."

00:41:15.660 --> 00:41:16.960
But they're kind of perfect.

00:41:16.960 --> 00:41:19.730
So I will never be a
